# Optional. Inlined at **build** time — change requires `npm run build` + redeploy.
# Leave unset for production: the app uses same-origin `/api/` (proxy API on the same host).
# For local dev, leave unset (defaults to http://localhost:4000/api) or set explicitly:
# VITE_API_URL="http://localhost:4000"
# VITE_API_URL="https://api.example.com/api"